# CHANGELOG.md is the one file where every PR genuinely just appends a
# new bullet to an additive section, so merge=union (which concatenates
# both sides of any textual conflict instead of emitting conflict
# markers) keeps multi-PR merges noise-free without defeating review.
# Apply this attribute ONLY to files where every change is purely
# additive — for anything else, union-merge silently smuggles non-
# additive edits past reviewers.
CHANGELOG.md merge=union
